snippet.title: Need for Speed Most Wanted | Ultimate Speed Pack DLC
snippet.description:
Watch the trailer for the Ultimate Speed Pack. Turbocharge your Need for Speed Most Wanted with a DLC pack showcasing five of the world's fastest exotics.
 
Boom! Here come the Pagani Zonda R, McLaren F1 LM, Bugatti Veyron Grand Sport Vitesse, Lamborghini Aventador J and Hennessey Venom GT Spyder. Take them on in high speed Races and Speed Runs: the perfect showcase for these mind-blowing cars. Beat the absurdly fast Hennessey Venom GT Spyder in an all-new Most Wanted List event and access extra rewards and unlocks in over 70 speed-themed Car Milestones
